high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the dresser.
Pick up the CD from the dresser.
Take a few steps to the left to face the alarm clock.
Open up the bottom drawer below the alarm clock and place the CD in it.
Look up at the CD next to the lamp.
Pick up the CD.
Look down towards the drawer below the alarm clock.
Open up the bottom drawer below the alarm clock and place the CD in it.
anns.task_desc: Place the CDs inside the bottom drawer below the alarm clock.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the right side of the white dresser that's in front of the bed.
Pick up the compact disc that's next to the pen.
Walk to the opposite side of the same dresser.
Open the bottom drawer on the left, place the compact disc in the drawer, and close it.
Stand in front of the mirror to the left of the dresser, and turn right to face the lamp.
Pick up the compact disc that's to the right of the lamp.
Walk to the front and left side of the dresser
Open the bottom drawer and put the compact disc to the right of the first compact disc.
anns.task_desc: Put two compact discs away in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn left, walk to the dresser to the left, and stop at the dresser in front of the compact disc.
Pick up the compact disc next to the pen.
Move to the left side of the dresser.
Open the bottom drawer on the left side of the dresser, place the compact disc in the back of the drawer and to the left, and close the drawer.
Walk to the mirror and turn right to face the lamp on the dresser.
Pick up the compact disc to the right of the lamp.
Move to the front left side of the dresser.
Open the bottom dresser drawer on the left, place the compact disc to the right of the first compact disc, and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put two compact discs in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn to your left and face the right side of the chest of drawers
Pick up the CD off of the top of the chest of drawers
Move to the left side of the chest of drawers
Open the second drawer from the bottom and put the cd in it
Move left and then turn to your right to face the side of the chest of drawers
Pick up another CD off of the top of the chest of drawers
Move back to where you were standing on the left side of the chest of the drawers
Open the second drawer from the bottom and put the other cd in it

high_descs: Go left, to the dresser.
Pick up the disc from the right side of the dresser.
Move to the left side of the dresser.
Open the second drawer up from the floor and put the disc in the left side of the drawer.
Continue to your left, around to the side of the dresser, with your left side to the wall.
Pick up the disc that is to the right of the lamp.
Move to your right, back to the left front of the dresser.
Put the disc away in the second drawer from the bottom, to the right of the first disc.
anns.task_desc: Put two discs away in a dresser drawer.
